Articles.Content:
Hello

I built this Apollo style craft a while ago. I flew it again to take pictures and post them.

Here it is:

http://imgur.com/a/3MGec
Nicely done! I appreciate the 2 stage lander, only then it counts as Apollo style in my opinion. Well done!
That was the most in depth set of pictures I have ever seen! Great work on the build man, I love the launch tower.
